These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, pop
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, drama
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
2. the fan of blues is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Flower       | zinnia       | daisy |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Music-Genre       | pop    | blues    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama       | western      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
City: paris, prague
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, australian
2 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the colombian is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| City      | prague     | paris |
| Nationality           | colombian | australian      |
| Pet   | mouse  | turtle      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
2 different games are played: poker, canasta
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, fantasy
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, purple
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who likes purple##1
3. the person playing poker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Game          | poker    | canasta   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | thriller   |
| Color     | purple     | grey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
House: craftsman, victorian
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, motorbike
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, zombie
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the victorian house is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| House      | craftsman       | victorian |
| Transport          | motorbike         | scooter    |
| Job           | security-guard | nurse    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy           | zombie   |

