There 2 different types of food: orange, papaya
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | skydiving | video-games   |
| Flower   | marigold | azalea       |
| Pet         | ferret   | guinea-pig |
| Food     | papaya    | orange     |

