.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, october
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, electronic
2 different games are played: whist, chess
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, van
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the fan of indie##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person playing whist is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Birthday           | october | april     |
| Music-Genre   | indie          | electronic |
| Game           | whist          | chess    |
| Transport     | van            | bus       |

 